### `flatprofiler compress`

Profile index compression.

```bash
# Profile compression
flatprofiler compress ./data

# High compression level
flatprofiler compress ./data --level 9

# Multi-worker
flatprofiler compress ./data --workers 8
```

**Sample Output:**

```
